title: Best Of The Dan Patrick Show: 11/27/2020
itunes:title: Best Of The Dan Patrick Show: 11/27/2020
description:
Jason McIntyre and Rob debate which quarterback they would rather having going forward; Lamar Jackson or Kyler Murray. Jason and Rob debate whether or not Tom Brady was the right fit in Tampa Bay. Plus they speak with Tyler Dunne, founder of ‘Go Long’, about the important of keeping longform journalism alive. The guys are also joined by former NFL and college football coach June Jones about the biggest stories from around the NFL!
